     <widget class="QWidget" name="tabAutocompleteSettings">
      <attribute name="title">
       <string>设置</string>
      </attribute>
      <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="layoutAutocompleteSettings">
       <item>
        <widget class="QGroupBox" name="groupAutocompleteSettings">
         <property name="title">
          <string>自动补全</string>
         </property>
         <layout class="QFormLayout" name="formAutocompleteSettings">
          <item row="0" column="0">
           <widget class="QLabel" name="lblAutocompleteLimit">
            <property name="text">
             <string>候选显示数量</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item row="0" column="1">
           <widget class="QSpinBox" name="spinAutocompleteLimit">
            <property name="minimum">
             <number>1</number>
            </property>
            <property name="maximum">
             <number>50</number>
            </property>
            <property name="value">
             <number>12</number>
            </property>
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>编辑提示词时自动补全弹窗最多显示的候选数量。</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item row="1" column="0" colspan="2">
           <widget class="QLabel" name="lblAutocompleteHint">
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string>在“提示词生成”和“模板与占位管理”中编辑提示词时，输入会自动弹出候选词（含翻译）。候选来源于已加载的翻译词表，兼容 a1111 与 ComfyUI 词表格式。</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item row="2" column="0" colspan="2">
           <widget class="QLabel" name="lblAutocompleteEnableHint">
            <property name="text">
